  "summary": "Malicious code in qbo-ui-services (npm)",
  "details": "A 534-byte \"placeholder\" package whose manifest declares a self-dependency at the non-registry URL hxxps://repo[.]securityctrl[.]com/qbo-ui-services. Installing it makes npm fetch a tarball from that attacker-controlled host for the qbo-ui-services dependency, enabling arbitrary code delivery at install time. The package claims to \"prevent dependency confusion\" but actually introduces it via a non-registry self-dependency URL.",
